sub_title: MSc Public Health Student at Lund University
summary:
I am a MSc. Public Health student at Lund University, Sweden with a special interest in international health policy development in the field of sexual and reproductive health and rights. 
My various practical and international experiences are the basis for my time management, organisational, teamwork and adaptability skills, as well as communicative, proactive and structured working style. Furthermore, during my academic career I was able to refine my professional knowledge and my research and analytical skills.
